disease: This could be a sign of Alcoholic hepatitis.

disease: This could be a sign of Tuberculosis.

What could it be?
disease: This could be a sign of Common Cold.

disease: This could be a sign of Pneumonia.

disease: This could be a sign of Heart attack.

disease: This could be a sign of Varicose veins.

symptoms: I have fatigue and mood swings and weight loss and restlessness and sweating and diarrhoea and fast heart rate and excessive hunger and muscle weakness and irritability and abnormal menstruation. What could it be?
